com.veepoo.protocol.model.settings

types ScreenSetting

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.veepoo.protocol.model.settings.ScreenSetting

  • public class ScreenSetting
extends java.lang.Object
    screen brightness setting, the screen brightness has a certain level, the current setting is[1-8]files, of which1stops have the lowest brightness,8levels of brightness

    We recommend [22:00-07:00] Set to2gear, set to other times4stops,

    The parameters passed to the constructor are{22,0,7,0,2,4}

    Created by Administrator on 2017/3/8.
